{"TopicId":177766,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Newbie question on mods","CreatedByName":"mr2005","CreatedById":191410,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-22T21:43:19Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"mr2005","CreatedById":191410,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-22T21:43:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello,\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m new to Kerbal. I\u0027m trying to figure out how to install mods. I purchased KErbal directly from the website and am running it on a windows 10 pc.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni\u0027ve seen how to vids on installing mods if you but through other avenues.\u00A0 \u00A0any suggestions for a newbie?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snark","CreatedById":125662,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-22T22:13:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello, and welcome to the forums!\u00A0 \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EMoving question to Add-on Discussions.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223438389\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022177766\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221534974199\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022191410\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022mr2005\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n27 minutes ago, mr2005 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m new to Kerbal. I\u0027m trying to figure out how to install mods. I purchased KErbal directly from the website and am running it on a windows 10 pc.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni\u0027ve seen how to vids on installing mods if you but through other avenues.\u00A0 \u00A0any suggestions for a newbie?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere\u0027s a FAQ with a \u0022how to run mods\u0022 section in it that you may find helpful:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed3461021160\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/171097-faq/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:228px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nExecutive summary is that you can install them manually, or (for mods that support it) with a \u0022mod manager\u0022 tool called \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Comprehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003ECKAN\u003C/abbr\u003E.\u00A0 Details in the above-linked post.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTo manually install a mod, you download it (generally as a .zip file) and unzip the contents into your GameData folder, then it \u0022just works\u0022.\u00A0 Uninstalling is easy, just delete the folder you added.\u00A0 Installing a mod takes effect the next time you start KSP.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bigcalm","CreatedById":143587,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-22T22:24:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHuge recommendation for\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/154922-ckan-the-comprehensive-kerbal-archive-network-v1252-goddard/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Comprehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003ECKAN\u003C/abbr\u003E \u003C/a\u003Ehere - it simplifies things enormously by allowing you to click and select mods in a simple GUI - and removing them is just as simple.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tyko","CreatedById":164179,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-22T22:32:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/187982-4x4cheesecake/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022187982\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/187982-4x4cheesecake/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@4x4cheesecake\u003C/a\u003E just wrote up a really good explanation in the forum post linked below.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed6726857916\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/177635-how-do-i-download-mods/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:226px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}